  <brief_title>Vitamin C Supplementation Plus Hypoglycemic Agents Versus Hypoglycemic Agents Alone in Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus</brief_title>
  <acronym>Vit C</acronym>
  <official_title>Phase 1 Study of Randomized Clinical Trial Comparing Vitamin C Supplementation Plus Oral Hypoglycemic Drugs Versus Hypoglycemic Drugs Alone on Serum Selenium, Zinc, Copper and Malondialdehyde Levels in Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus and Its Microvascular Complications</official_title>
