  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Null hypothesis:

      No significant effect of vitamin C 500 mg Supplementation on the severity of micro-vascular
      complications of type 2 Diabetes Mellitus (DM).

      Alternative hypothesis:

      There is a significant effect of vitamin C 500mg supplementation on the severity of the
      micro-vascular complications of type 2DM.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
