  </intervention>
  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  clinical diagnosis of type 2DM

          -  patients in good health

          -  receiving oral hypoglycemic drugs

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Insulin dependent diabetes

          -  receiving vitamin complex

          -  smoking

          -  renal disease

          -  liver disease
      </textblock>
